mutation ($payload:BplusItSappiCreateChannelOverviewInput!)
{
	bplusItSappiCreateChannelOverview (payload:$payload)
	{
		id
		tenantId
		tenantCode
		systemId
		systemName
		executionId
		executionType
		executionExecutedAt
		executionMonitoringStartAt
		executionMonitoringEndAt
		error
		inactive
		successful
		stopped
		unknown
		unregistered
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}
